{"tid":808983,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"西洋流行曲之中 有冇人唱假音好聽得過 Bee Gees?","createTime":"2018-09-06T19:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T10:50:47.000Z","uid":60845,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0337c780a875789b849ccda8f4c9156b63601eca","tid":808983,"uid":60845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T19:00:00.000Z","msg":"大哥 Barry 把聲簡直係天籟<br />\n配合埋兩位細佬 Robin 同 Maurice 嘅完美和音<br />\n造就眾多經典<br />\n<br />\n要數代表作中嘅代表作<br />\n相信係以下兩首<br />\n<br />\nHow Deep Is Your Love (1977)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XpqqjU7u5Yc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXpqqjU7u5Yc&d=GWPW7JtnNR0n12GJohEXkZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=d193839d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XpqqjU7u5Yc</a><br />\n<br />\nToo Much Heaven (1978)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nREV8bQJ1MA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnREV8bQJ1MA&d=GWPW7JtnNR0n12GJohEXkZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=a2299ed5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nREV8bQJ1MA</a><br />\n<br />\n除左 Bee Gees 自己既作品<br />\n寫俾其他人然後一齊唱既歌 一樣係咁屈機<br />\n例如有<br />\n<br />\nSamantha Sang - Emotion (1977)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zPwpVJ-eIgg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzPwpVJ-eIgg&d=GWPW7JtnNR0n12GJohEXkZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=10ea3199\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zPwpVJ-eIgg</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有 30 歲就英年早逝嘅四弟 Andy Gibb<br />\n<br />\nAndy Gibb - (Our Love) Don't Throw It All Away (1978)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UNkZEX_iBY4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUNkZEX_iBY4&d=GWPW7JtnNR0n12GJohEXkZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=848b13fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UNkZEX_iBY4</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎留言挑機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3d3ac30e79aa2f5c41fbba844ac1b9ebf726cc","tid":808983,"uid":13821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T19:01:53.000Z","msg":"你呢條問題我前幾日先問完我老逗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老逗都話Bee Gees應該係唱得最好"},{"pid":"a6681bfb8cc447d8d1351236f292babca90a8778","tid":808983,"uid":60845,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1e3d3ac30e79aa2f5c41fbba844ac1b9ebf726cc","tid":808983,"uid":13821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T19:01:53.000Z","msg":"你呢條問題我前幾日先問完我老逗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我老逗都話Bee Gees應該係唱得最好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T19:13:07.000Z","msg":"唔單止好聽 仲極具影響力<br />\n當時可以話係帶領成個 Disco 熱潮<br />\n論標誌性 應該無第一都第二<br />\n可惜在生嘅已經得返大佬一個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f46326724c5d45b30eeef4b6b0c277db001040ff","tid":808983,"uid":80535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T19:52:18.000Z","msg":"Stayin Alive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b094cdb48f22fed7b8bb037ec0bce5ea043dd95f","tid":808983,"uid":60845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:15:10.000Z","msg":"得咁少懷舊 jj? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303860ef1709d28e08dbd8f2d1b5604a0801627e","tid":808983,"uid":8219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T02:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c7f4200ed44022fbd9ddb9ecdd17d7655b213db","tid":808983,"uid":206023,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"qu